title: Motoi Sakuraba Live Concert: Star Ocean, Valkyrie Profile (2003)
description:
Motoi Sakuraba Live Concert Star Ocean & Valkyrie Profile

Description

On July 19, 2003 at Zepp Tokyo, Motoi Sakuraba held his first live concert. A
two hour progressive rock experience, Sakuraba led a trio to perform various
works from tri-Ace's Star Ocean series and Valkyrie Profile.

Production

Original composition and arrangement by Motoi Sakuraba

Performance

Motoi Sakuraba (10 Keyboards)
Toshihiko Nakamura (Drums)
Atsushi Hasegawa (Bass Guitar)

Set Listings

01) The Dawn of Wisdom [Star Ocean Till the End of Time]
02) Unfinished Battle with God Syndrome [Valkyrie Profile]
03) Fly Away in the Violet Sky [Star Ocean Till the End of Time]
04) Reflected Moon [Star Ocean Till the End of Time]
05) Hand in Hand [Star Ocean Blue Sphere]
06) Requiem to a Predicament ~ Falling Under Negative Consciousness ~ [Valkyrie Profile]
07) March for Glory [Star Ocean Till the End of Time]
08) Theme of RENA [Star Ocean The Second Story] ~ Drum Solo ~ Bass Solo ~
09) Highbrow [Star Ocean Till the End of Time]
10) So Alone, Be Sorrow [Star Ocean Till the End of Time]
11) Mission to the Deep Space [Star Ocean Till the End of Time]
12) Confidence in the Domination [Star Ocean Till the End of Time]
13) Cutting Edge of Notion [Star Ocean Till the End of Time]
14) Doorway to Heaven [Valkyrie Profile]

Encore

15) STAR OCEAN FOREVER ~ The Incarnation of Devil ~ The Dawn of Wisdom

Included: Bonus Studio Recording, Interviews, and Concert Commentary

Audio: MP3 VBR 2ch 48kHz (avconv -q0 from LPCM/AC3 sources)
Language: Japanese
